OL,3,CMajor step for #10bn investment in
OL,4,CNorthumberland as data centre plans
OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,FLandmark proposals that would see one
OL,8,Fof the largest ever foreign
OL,9,Finvestments in the UK come to
OL,10,FNorthumberland have taken a
OL,11,Fsignificant step forward after outline
OL,12,Fplanning permission to build a data
OL,13,Fcentre campus was granted.
OL,15,FThe major development would consist of
OL,16,F10 separate buildings totalling
OL,17,F540,000sqm of floor space built on the
OL,18,Fsite of the former coal-fired Blyth
OL,19,FPower Station, near Cambois.
