OL,3,CMajor step for #10bn investment in
OL,4,CNorthumberland as data centre plans
OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,FTotal investment in the site from US
OL,8,Ffirm QTS could reach #10bn, the Local
OL,9,FDemocracy Reporting Service reports.
OL,11,FMembers of the council's strategic
OL,12,Fplanning committee voted unanimously
OL,13,Fto approve the plans on Tuesday (4
OL,14,FMarch). Further details will need to
OL,15,Fbe confirmed in a series of future
OL,16,Fplanning applications before
OL,17,Fconstruction can begin.
