OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,FMembers were told that the buildings
OL,8,Fwill reach a maximum height of 35
OL,9,Fmetres, and provide 72 megawatts of
OL,10,Fcapacity per building to power
OL,11,Ftechnology such as cloud storage and
OL,12,FAI systems. Each building will require
OL,13,Faround 40 staff on completion,
OL,14,Ftotalling 400 specialised employees
OL,15,Fonce fully built out.
OL,17,FQTS has committed to sourcing staff
OL,18,Ffrom within a 25 mile radius of the
OL,19,Fsite. In addition, it is estimated
OL,20,Fthat the project will create 1,200
OL,21,Flong-term construction jobs.
