OL,7,F"There is an urgent need for these
OL,8,Fhugely important facilities. Cambois
OL,9,Fis exceptionally well suited to a
OL,10,Flarge-scale data centre campus, given
OL,11,Fthe extensive land area, connectivity
OL,12,Fto high capacity electrical
OL,13,Finfrastructure and access to local
OL,14,Femployment.
