OL,7,F"This will be a significant investment
OL,8,Fof up to #10 billion over the lifetime
OL,9,Fof the project ` one of the largest in
OL,10,Fthe UK. This is not our first project
OL,11,F` we know how to partner with
OL,12,Fcommunities and we want this
OL,13,Fpartnership to be deep and enduring."
OL,15,FAs part of the application, the
OL,16,Fapplicant has agreed to fund the
OL,17,Fcreation of an education, employment
OL,18,Fand training plan covering both the
OL,19,Fconstruction and operation phase. This
OL,20,Fwill ensure local people have the
OL,21,Fskills needed to work in the facility.
