OL,4,CNorthumberland as data centre plans
OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,FThe data centre plan came forward
OL,8,Fafter previous proposals for an
OL,9,Felectric car battery factory never
OL,10,Fcame to fruition. The company behind
OL,11,Fthe scheme, Britishvolt, collapsed
OL,12,Finto administration.
OL,14,FReferencing Tory Councillor Richard
OL,15,FDodd added: "I welcome this. I was
OL,16,Fsceptical of the previous application
OL,17,F` it was too good to be true with the
OL,18,Fthousands of jobs promised and nothing
OL,19,Fever came.
OL,26,@wD@MOU
