OL,7,F"But this has a different feel, it
OL,8,Ffeels like it will take place and
OL,9,Fwe're going to get something. I only
OL,10,Fhope national politicians remember how
OL,11,Fit came about when they try to take
OL,12,Fcredit."
OL,14,FLabour's local ward councillor Alex
OL,15,FWallace added: "In 1968, the coal mine
OL,16,Fclosed. Two thousand people left the
OL,17,Farea to find work.
OL,19,F"We are now saying we are going to
OL,20,Fprovide that work for their
OL,21,Fgrandchildren. I'm just over the moon."
