OL,7,F"This proud corner of Northumberland
OL,8,Fwill be home to one of western
OL,9,FEurope's largest data hubs ` a multi-
OL,10,Fbillion-pound vote of confidence in
OL,11,Four county's future. We can now look
OL,12,Fforward to work progressing as this
OL,13,Fonce-in-a-lifetime opportunity takes
OL,14,Fshape in Northumberland.
OL,16,F"I am very grateful to Blackstone and
